## User

Type: [Object][71]

### Properties

*   `id` **[string][72]** The unique identifier of the user.
*   `createdAt` **[string][72]** The timestamp indicating when the user was created.
*   `email` **[string][72]** The email address of the user.
*   `admin` **[boolean][73]** Indicates whether the user has admin privileges.
*   `password` **([string][72] | null)** The password of the user (nullable for security reasons).
